================================================================================
UPDATE HEALTH RULES
================================================================================

RED

Use Red whenever ANY condition applies.

• Unassigned issue

• Current assignee has NEVER updated

• Assignee meaningful update older than 5 business days

• Requester followed up after the assignee's last update and assignee has not responded

• Latest Jira update is from requester

• Latest Jira update is from manager

• Latest Jira update is from automation

• Jira appears active but assignee has not updated

• Only acknowledgement comments exist

• Blocked with no ETA

• Blocked with no dependency owner

• In Progress but no meaningful assignee update

RED always overrides every other health.

AMBER

Use Amber when

Assignee updated between

3 and 5 business days ago

OR

Update lacks

ETA

