GREEN

Use Green ONLY when

Current assignee provided a meaningful update within the last TWO business days

AND

Requester follow-up (if any) has been answered afterward

AND

Update contains actual technical progress

Examples

Testing completed

Investigation complete

Deployment completed

Blocker identified

ETA

Next action

Logs

Evidence

Findings

Never classify Green solely because Jira Last Updated is recent.

